# Cloudflare Pages headers. Patterns and values per
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/.

# Baseline security headers for every response — closes TO_UPGRADE.md
# P1 #11 (no CSP) and adds HSTS / clickjack / sniff protections that
# Helmet already sets on the API side.
#
# CSP notes:
# - 'unsafe-eval' on script-src and worker-src is unfortunate but
#   required: Monaco's tokenizer compiles regex via `new Function()`
#   (https://github.com/microsoft/monaco-editor/issues/1325), and
#   Pyodide's bootstrap likewise uses eval-like constructs.
# - 'unsafe-inline' on style-src is needed for React's style={{...}}
#   props in a few places.
# - worker-src includes blob: because Monaco bundles its editor worker
#   as an inline blob URL via Vite's worker plugin.
# - cdn.jsdelivr.net is allowed for scripts + styles because
#   @monaco-editor/react fetches Monaco's own bundle from there at
#   runtime. Self-hosting Monaco is a P2 follow-up; until then, the
#   editor depends on this CDN.
# - static.cloudflareinsights.com + cloudflareinsights.com are CF
#   Pages' built-in Web Analytics. Disable in CF dashboard if you
#   don't want this and we can remove the allowlist entry.
# - fonts.googleapis.com (CSS) + fonts.gstatic.com (woff2) are loaded
#   alongside the CF Insights beacon. Self-host the fonts to remove.
# - connect-src lists Sentry's EU ingest hosts explicitly. If you
#   move Sentry projects to a different region, update the pattern.
# - img-src allows data: for inline SVG icons; font-src allows data:
#   for any base64-embedded fonts Monaco or other libs ship.
/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=31536000; includeSubDomains
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=()
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-eval' 'wasm-unsafe-eval' https://cdn.jsdelivr.net https://static.cloudflareinsights.com; worker-src 'self' blob:; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://cdn.jsdelivr.net https://fonts.googleapis.com; img-src 'self' data:; font-src 'self' data: https://fonts.gstatic.com; connect-src 'self' https://api.learncode.study https://*.sentry.io https://*.ingest.sentry.io https://*.ingest.de.sentry.io https://*.ingest.us.sentry.io https://cloudflareinsights.com; frame-ancestors 'none'; base-uri 'self'; form-action 'self' https://accounts.google.com https://www.facebook.com

# Pyodide runtime files are version-pinned in the path (we don't change
# them until we upgrade Pyodide), so cache them aggressively. ~13 MB
# total; without this they'd re-download on every page load.
/pyodide/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
